        "prerequisite": "*Magaambyan Attendant Dedication*",
        "access": "You\u2019re a member of the Vellumis Scholars.",
        "cost": "1 spirit wisp",
        "effect": "You immediately purify a spirit, which grants you a protective blessing before it departs. If your next action is to cast a halcyon spell, you gain a +1 status bonus to saving throws as well as resistance to void damage equal to the rank of the halcyon spell. These effects last for 1 round.  \n  \nEvery day before your daily preparations, any spirit wisps remaining within your *spirit dwelling* from the previous day are purified and can continue along the River of Souls.",
